[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     64[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The dose-titration check (`"should i take"`, `"should i increase"`, `"should i lower"`) is third in the chain and never reached. The medication-discrepancy response that fires instead happens to pass output-safety screening because:
